### Example 8.35: Plot the quadratic fit

```scheme
(define xs (list 0 1 2 3 4))
(define ys (list 1.1 2.8 6.2 11.1 17.9))

(define A
  (matrix/make
    (map (lambda (x)
           (list 1 x (* x x)))
         xs)))

(define y-vec (vec/make 1.1 2.8 6.2 11.1 17.9))

(define coeffs (linalg/least-squares A y-vec))
(define a (vec/ref coeffs 0))
(define b (vec/ref coeffs 1))
(define c (vec/ref coeffs 2))

(define fit-fn
  (lambda (x)
    (+ a (* b x) (* c x x))))

(define points
  (map (lambda (x y) (geom/point x y)) xs ys))

(plot/render-svg
  (plot/with
    (plot/scatter points)
    (plot/function fit-fn -0.5 4.5)))
```
